<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Top left hand corner of a moulded, <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.42</measure>   × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre" precision="circa">0.25</measure> x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.22</measure>), broken into two (adjoining) parts.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face, in the panel inset by the moulding; the text appears to be centred.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Finely cut, standard forms; l. 1, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.04</measure>; l. 2, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03</measure>, ll. 3-4, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.025</measure>. Stop after <foreign lang="grc">ΚΑΡΜ</foreign> in l. 2.
</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p>
</div>
